Subject: [PATCH 3/3] Replace sudo with pkexec

---
 arb/intl_en.arb                   |  1 -
 lib/common/system.dart            | 41 +++++++++++++++----------------
 lib/l10n/intl/messages_en.dart    |  3 ---
 lib/l10n/intl/messages_ja.dart    |  3 ---
 lib/l10n/intl/messages_ru.dart    |  3 ---
